<http://www.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/event/181001ATMRVKTCRDBKKTKLKBKNCGJRLSH> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "CVIFF 2026 Feature - Akashi";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Akashi</span><span><br/></span>(CVIFF 2026 - Feature Film) <span><br/></span>2025, Canada, Japan, 100 minutes, Japanese & English <span><br/></span>Directed by: Mayumi Yoshida <span><br/></span>Cast:  Hana Kino, Ryo Tajima, Sayaka Kunisada, Bun Kimura, Yuriko Onuma, Mayumi Yoshida, Hiro Kanagawa, Jess McLeod<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Akashi</span><span><br/></span>When Kana, a Japanese artist living in Vancouver, returns to Tokyo for her grandmother’s funeral, she finds herself caught between two worlds - the life she’s built abroad and the one she left behind. As family expectations close in and an old flame, Hiro, reappears, Kana begins to question where she truly belongs.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>She also uncovers traces of a long-buried family secret – a love that defied time and tradition. Drawn into the mystery, Kana begins to see her family’s past reflected in her own life, blurring the lines between memory, self, duty, and desire. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>At the recent Whistler Film Festival, Mayumi Yoshida won best actor, best BC director, and the Haebler Award for best feature. Jaryl Lim won for best cinematography.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Stay afterwards for a Q&A with the filmmakers!</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">This film is not rated. Intended for mature audiences. May include strong language and or scenes and themes some viewers may find disturbing.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">About CVIFF</span> <span><br/></span>The Comox Valley International Film Festival (CVIFF) is a non-profit organization that discovers and supports independent films from around the world and introduces them to audiences. We believe in the power of a good story! <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://cviff.ca/\"> cviff.ca</a><span><br/></span>
""";
