<http://www.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/event/180201ARDPVDMGSBDRHNKHPMBCHGHNCHQ> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "CVIFF 2026 Festival Pass";
  schema:description """
	Immerse yourself in all the films and activities the festival offers. With a festival pass you can see all of the films, Q&As, script readings, and more!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>DAY 1 </h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Opening Night Feature - The Art of Adventure</span> <span><br/></span>Thu April 2 at 7:00pm <span><br/></span>Canada<span><br/></span>86 minutes <span><br/></span>English <span><br/></span>See full details <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.sidwilliamstheatre.com/events/cviff-2026-opening-night-the-art-of-adventure/\"> The Art of Adventure</a> <span><br/></span><span><br/></span> <span><br/></span><h2>DAY 2 </h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Short Films – Canada’s Best</span> <span><br/></span>Fri April 3 at 10:00am <span><br/></span>111 minutes plus Q & A. <span><br/></span>See full details <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.sidwilliamstheatre.com/events/cviff-2026-short-films-canadas-best/\"> Canada’s Best</a> <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Short Films – Best of The Island and Beyond</span> <span><br/></span>Fri April 3 at 1:00pm <span><br/></span>125 minutes plus Q & A. <span><br/></span>See full details <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.sidwilliamstheatre.com/events/cviff-2026-short-films-best-of-the-island-and-beyond/\"> Best of The Island and Beyonds</a> <span><br/></span><span><br/></span> <span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Feature Film – Akashi</span> <span><br/></span>Fri April 3 at 7:00pm <span><br/></span>Canada, Japan<span><br/></span>100 minutes plus Q & A.<span><br/></span>Japanese, English <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>See full details <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.sidwilliamstheatre.com/events/cviff-2026-feature-akashi/\"> Akashi</a> <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>DAY 3 </h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Short Films – Around The World</span> <span><br/></span>Sat April 4 at 10:00am <span><br/></span>154 minutes<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>See full details <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.sidwilliamstheatre.com/events/cviff-2026-short-films-around-the-world/\"> Around The World</a> <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Feature Film – Saints and Warriors</span> <span><br/></span>Sat April 4 at 1:30pm <span><br/></span>Canada<span><br/></span>99 minutes plus Q & A.<span><br/></span>English <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>See full details <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.sidwilliamstheatre.com/events/cviff-2026-feature-saints-and-warriors/\"> Saints and Warriors</a> <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Closing Night Feature – Dancing On The Elephant</span> <span><br/></span>Sat April 4 at 7:00pm <span><br/></span>Canada<span><br/></span>94 minutes<span><br/></span>English <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>See full details <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.sidwilliamstheatre.com/events/cviff-2026-closing-night-dancing-on-the-elephant/\"> Dancing On The Elephant</a> <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">About CVIFF</span> <span><br/></span>The Comox Valley International Film Festival (CVIFF) is a non-profit organization that discovers and supports independent films from around the world and introduces them to audiences. We believe in the power of a good story! <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://cviff.ca/\"> cviff.ca</a><span><br/></span>
""";
