<http://www.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/event/180002APTKRTNMKRVPTGDPKSLKMNDLHPB> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "CVIFF 2026 Short Films - Around The World";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">CVIFF 2026 Short Film Programming – Around the World</span><span><br/></span>Canada, International, 154 minutes<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>A tender portrait of finding love, even at the end of life. Two young boys who fight make-believe monsters…while real-life monsters lurk nearby. An ancient board game explodes into an animated treat for the senses. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>These are some of the amazing short films we’ve found from across Canada and around the world. Sometimes the best things come in small packages. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Titles:</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">The Hermit <span><br/></span>Take it Off <span><br/></span>Last Resort <span><br/></span>Pardesi <span><br/></span>Unfrayed <span><br/></span>Winners & Losers <span><br/></span>The Hand of God <span><br/></span>The Dandelion Girl <span><br/></span>Our Monsters <span><br/></span>Midnight Murungai <span><br/></span>Don’t Be Rude <span><br/></span>The Peculiar Sleeping Pattern of Edgar Hick</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Please note: programming subject to change.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Warning:</span> <span class=\"ItalicText\">Short films are unrated. Intended for mature audiences. May include strong language and or scenes and themes some viewers may find disturbing.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">About CVIFF</span> <span><br/></span>The Comox Valley International Film Festival (CVIFF) is a non-profit organization that discovers and supports independent films from around the world and introduces them to audiences. We believe in the power of a good story! <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://cviff.ca/\"> cviff.ca</a><span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-04-04T10:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
