<http://www.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/event/180801ACNRNVTNLQTNBRHMMHMPGLDKJCB> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "CVIFF 2026 Short Films - Best of The Island and Beyond";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">CVIFF 2026 Short Film Programming – Best of The Island and Beyond</span>  <span><br/></span>Canada, 125 minutes, English<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From a lonely Cyclops looking for a friend, to a young woman coming to terms with her traumatic past, the short films in this block celebrate original storytelling from Vancouver Island. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>We also celebrate filmmakers from the rest of the country – including the story of a nightclub magician…who might be more than he seems. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Filmmakers in attendance!</span> Stay after for a Q&A.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For more information about the films, filmmakers, workshops, and festival, please visit <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://cviff.ca/\"> cviff.ca</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Titles:</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Enzo My Familiar <span><br/></span>The Ballad of Sloth Shot  <span><br/></span>Spark Bird <span><br/></span>Knots <span><br/></span>The Children Are Afraid <span><br/></span>The Magician <span><br/></span>Oob: The Last Cyclops <span><br/></span>Last Night Together <span><br/></span>Notes From A Poet</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Please note: programming subject to change.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Warning:</span> <span class=\"ItalicText\">Short films are unrated. Intended for mature audiences. May include strong language and or scenes and themes some viewers may find disturbing.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">About CVIFF</span> <span><br/></span>The Comox Valley International Film Festival (CVIFF) is a non-profit organization that discovers and supports independent films from around the world and introduces them to audiences. We believe in the power of a good story! <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://cviff.ca/\"> cviff.ca</a><span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-04-03T13:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
