<http://www.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/event/182201AKLHSBJGPRBLJBLDPLKPHGJSQQC> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Director's Cut 20th Anniversary Highlights (Virtual)";
  schema:description """
	<h2>Virtual Event</h2><span><br/></span>As part of their milestone 20th Anniversary Season, Just in Time Choirs continue the celebration with their spring concert, <span class=\"ItalicText\">“Director’s Cut – 20th Anniversary Highlights.”</span><span><br/></span> <span><br/></span>For two decades, the Just in Time Choirs have been bringing community together through the power of song; sharing music, connection, and unforgettable performances. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This spring concert marks Part 2 of their anniversary concert series, featuring a collection of personal favourites from Musical Director Wendy Nixon Stothert. Drawing from standout moments across the past twenty years, Director’s Cut showcases songs that have shaped the choir’s musical journey. From audience favourites to meaningful repertoire, and highlights that reflect the growth and spirit of the choir family. This concert continues a year-long celebration honouring 20 years of music and community. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join Just in Time Choirs as they look back on cherished memories while celebrating the vibrant energy that continues to inspire singers and audiences alike. Come celebrate the music, the memories, and the next chapter of Just in Time Choirs.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-04-25T19:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
