<http://www.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/event/182401AVQRJLLQKJHHRHJLQDDLMVNBNDL> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Fairytales and Myths Oh My!";
  schema:description """
	When the enchanted Storybook Compass glitches, characters from fairy tales, nursery rhymes and Norse myths suddenly find themselves lost in the wrong stories. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Cinderella, Goldilocks, and even the Big Bad Wolf are thrown into hilarious confusion as worlds collide in the Storybook Realm. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Performers ages 3–16 bring this magical mishap to life as heroes, sprites, princesses and creatures who must work together to set the stories right. With courage, teamwork and a spark of imagination, they just might restore the happily ever after.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">About Sitka Stage & Screen</span><span><br/></span>Sitka Stage & Screen provides an educational and nurturing environment where students can learn about the joys of acting, find their confidence, and strengthen their performance skills while exploring the world of theatre and film. 
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-06-28T14:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
