<http://www.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/event/182801AGDVQGPQKDBLBDNPQLGDVNGTVGQ> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Ignite 2026";
  schema:description """
	Join Triple Heat Dance (THD) Academy of Performing Arts as they present their 14th Annual Year End Showcase, Ignite 2026! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This highly anticipated annual event celebrates the hard work, passion, and dedication of the incredible dancers and faculty throughout the season. Enjoy two action-packed showcases, filled with energy, creativity, and unforgettable performances. With each class performing twice, you’ll have the chance to see every routine shine on stage. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The dancers, ages 2–19, will light up the stage in a wide range of styles including ballet, jazz, hip hop, contemporary, lyrical, tap, variety, and song & dance. From the tiniest performers taking their first brave steps under the stage lights, to the senior dancers delivering powerful, polished performances, this show truly highlights the growth and artistry of the entire THD community.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The showcases will feature award-winning competition pieces, exciting group numbers, and some of the sweetest Little Feet classes that are sure to melt your heart. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Ignite 2026 promises to be an exhilarating, family-friendly event for all ages, celebrating the spirit, talent, and passion that make the Triple Heat Dance community so special. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Come cheer on our dancers and experience the magic of a full season brought to life on stage.<span><br/></span>
""";
