  schema:name "Season Kickoff & 25th Anniversary Reception";
  schema:description """
	Join theatre society staff and board members as we celebrate the 25th anniversary of the Sid Williams Theatre Society and prepare to kick off our 25th season of programming.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This reception will be open house style from 7pm - 9pm.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Complimentary refreshments include a selection of desserts (CAKE!) and beverages.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>There will be prize draws too - including the chance to win a pair of tickets to the <span class=\"UnderlineText\">entire</span> 2025 - 2026 Blue Circle Series. That's over <span class=\"UnderlineText\">$1800</span> worth of tickets!
""";
