<http://www.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/event/179001AHMHLVDRHJDLMNNLCQJJHJJCLJH> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Shine 2026 by Pantuso Dance";
  schema:description """
	Pantuso Dance is proud to present <span class=\"ItalicText\">Shine 2026</span>, a dynamic showcase celebrating the commitment, growth, and artistry of our Pantuso Performance Works dancers. Experience an inspiring evening as outstanding soloists, duos, trios, Broadway Jazz teens and adults, and the powerful Pantuso Studio Ensemble take the stage. Each performance reflects countless hours of dedication and the vision of leading choreographers who continue to shape and elevate our artists. Join us for a captivating night of movement, expression, and excellence that truly shines.
""";
