<http://www.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/event/177801ATGGBLKVDRTLQTSPRKHJLRNHSTR> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Three for the Tillerman: An Intimate Tribute to Cat Stevens";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"ItalicText\">Three for the Tillerman</span> is a heartfelt tribute to the timeless music of Cat Stevens. Led by vocalist and musician Pierre Trépanier, alongside Alain Couture and Martin Lessard, the trio delivers a warm and captivating acoustic performance featuring guitars, piano, bass, percussion, flute, and rich vocal harmonies.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With intimate staging and thoughtful storytelling, the show preserves the original spirit of Cat Stevens’ most beloved songs while offering fresh, expressive interpretations. Audiences are invited into a cozy, living-room atmosphere for an evening filled with nostalgia, connection, and the enduring beauty of melodies that have touched generations.
""";
