<http://www.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/event/179201APGTCQQVPDMSKJGSSMRBNDJJQNR> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "VanCity Bhangra";
  schema:description """
	Established in 2012, VanCity Bhangra offers a hybrid style of Bhangra. Keeping the traditional form and folk elements and mixing them with unique style of high energy actions is what they bring to the table. VanCity Bhangra performances capture the audience’s hearts with gimmicks, stunts, and exhilarating Bhangra. They love performing for many reasons, being able to meet new people and showcasing hard work. They hope you find influence in their routine to follow a dream.
""";
