<http://www.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/event/184601ARLMKLDPDCBVNPLLVTCPPNDQKHP> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Weeds Through the Pavement: CVAG Youth Media Project Screening";
  schema:description """
	Join the CVAG Youth Media Project for some newly created films by emerging young filmmakers!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The Comox Valley Art Gallery’s Youth Media Project uses digital media, creative facilitation, and artistic collaboration as a framework for youth to create media for community action. Those who come through the program end up creating long-lasting connections not just with each other, but with other community members and organizations in the Comox Valley. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">“The Comox Valley Art Gallery’s Youth Media Project uplifts emerging creative change-makers and storytellers. It is an inclusive space where contemporary issues can be examined and where participants can make and share meaningful media.”</span><span><br/></span>- Team Leader Krista Tupper.
""";
